Package org.cast.cwm

Interface Summary
IEventLogger Interface for an object that can be used to log events.
IRelativeLinkSource An object (typically a Resource) that can be used to locate resources via relative links.
 

Class Summary
AbstractEventService Abstract base class for an event-logging functionality.
CwmApplication An abstract Application class that CWM-based apps can extend.
CwmIdGenerator Used by Hibernate Annotations to generate pooled IDs for stored objects.
CwmSession Extension of Databinder's AuthDataSession that keeps track of the LoginSession.
CwmSessionStore A session store that adds a listener to do cleanup of CwmSession objects.
CwmSessionStore.CwmSessionBindingListener This is the listener attached to each session.
LoggingEventService Basic implementation of AbstractEventService that logs events as DEBUG messages in the console.
